        public static AssertJJsonValueAssert.AssertJJsonValuePromiseAssert assertThat(Promise<JsonValue,?> promise)

        On calling the succeeded method, the AssertJJsonValueAssert.AbstractJsonValueAssert.isObject() and AssertJJsonValueAssert.AbstractJsonValueAssert.isArray() must be used to access array/object specific assert methods.
